custom_test_report_genes.summary: No one rejects, dislikes, or avoids pleasure itself, because it is pleasure, but because those who do not know how to pursue pleasure rationally encounter consequences that are extremely painful.
But I must explain to you how all this mistaken idea of denouncing pleasure and praising pain was born and I will give you a complete account.

custom_test_report_result.result: One Pathogenic variant identified in RAD50. RAD50 is associated with autosomal dominant hereditary breast cancer and autosomal recessive Nijmegen breakage syndrome-like disorder. Additional Variant(s) of Uncertain Significance identified.

custom_test_report_interpretation.interpretation: This result is consistent with a predisposition to, or diagnosis of, autosomal dominant RAD50-related conditions.
